WEBVTT

00:06.868 --> 00:09.704
- What the hell's wrong with you?
- No, I'm just saying.

00:09.788 --> 00:11.289
They do weird shit with Mrs. Butterworth.

00:11.372 --> 00:13.252
They shouldn't have shaped
her bottle like that.

00:15.835 --> 00:17.921
I hate to hear what you do to donuts.

00:21.883 --> 00:23.593
Well... there's Dad.

00:25.053 --> 00:27.346
Wonder how many cows
he inseminated today.

00:27.430 --> 00:28.973
Don't know. Don't care.

00:29.057 --> 00:30.975
He wants to take away
all the important jobs,

00:31.059 --> 00:32.435
treat me like a hired hand?

00:33.186 --> 00:35.438
I'm just gonna kick back,
get paid and drink beer.

00:35.522 --> 00:36.565
Hell yeah.

00:37.315 --> 00:39.859
Just like me when I
played for Florida State.

00:41.485 --> 00:42.612
I'd say, "We should go in there"

00:42.696 --> 00:44.322
and shave off his mustache
while he's asleep,"

00:44.405 --> 00:46.950
but it'd probably just grow
back before he wakes up.

00:48.910 --> 00:51.705
Look at him in there.
Washing dishes by hand.

00:51.788 --> 00:56.000
[imitating Beau] "Don't trust the
dishwasher to do a good enough job."

00:56.084 --> 00:58.628
Ain't got enough experience
washing dishes."

00:59.963 --> 01:01.130
We don't have a dishwasher.

01:03.507 --> 01:06.094
What the fuck have I been putting
all them dirty dishes in?

01:07.053 --> 01:09.263
I'm just kidding,
I know we ain't got one.

01:09.347 --> 01:11.390
Even if we did, he'd probably
curse out the Koreans

01:11.474 --> 01:15.519
for making the buttons too small
for his big, fat American fingers.

01:15.604 --> 01:17.856
Yeah. [Imitating Beau]
"What the hell is extra rinse?

01:17.939 --> 01:20.316
Why not just rinse 'em right
the first time, Kim Jong?"

01:20.399 --> 01:21.610
[Colt chuckles]

01:23.277 --> 01:25.029
Hey, you wanna head down to the bar?

01:25.113 --> 01:27.031
No, I gotta take a shower.

01:27.699 --> 01:29.408
Taking Abby out
on our first date tonight.

01:29.492 --> 01:31.285
- Ooh, all right.
- What are you doing?

01:31.369 --> 01:32.411
Going down to the bar.

01:32.495 --> 01:33.579
Depending on how the night goes,

01:33.663 --> 01:36.374
I'm either gonna hang out
with Mary or Mrs. Butterworth.

01:37.626 --> 01:39.711
And in a perfect world, both.

01:41.000 --> 01:47.074
-= www.OpenSubtitles.org =-

01:49.428 --> 01:51.014
You put that snow fence back up?

01:51.097 --> 01:52.682
