it up," so we did that.

01:57.729 --> 02:00.148
Yeah, we also moved that feed
trough to where you wanted it.

02:00.231 --> 02:02.191
Did the whole job and did it correctly.

02:02.275 --> 02:04.736
Like responsible,
intelligent adults, so...

02:04.819 --> 02:06.070
[blows raspberry]

02:08.531 --> 02:12.410
I know you're still bent out of shape
about me taking over the insemination.

02:13.494 --> 02:15.496
It might make you feel
better if you just...

02:16.497 --> 02:17.957
get the fuck over it.

02:19.292 --> 02:20.710
[blows raspberry]

02:24.839 --> 02:26.841
Hey, remember how pissed Dad got

02:26.925 --> 02:30.011
when I put that Hillary bumper
sticker on his tractor?

02:31.262 --> 02:33.014
Well, now I'm gonna
put one on his coffin.

02:38.186 --> 02:41.022
Oh, Mrs. Butterworth. [Sighs]

02:42.356 --> 02:43.942
I'm sorry about my brother.

02:45.568 --> 02:47.946
