- Here we go.

03:54.345 --> 03:56.848
- [Abby] Yeah, uh...
- You know where we are?

03:56.931 --> 03:58.141
Well, it smells good,

03:58.224 --> 04:00.226
so I'm guessing it's not your bedroom.

04:00.309 --> 04:01.685
