You know what might be better?

10:37.998 --> 10:39.041
Anything.

10:39.875 --> 10:42.336
What if we just stay in
and entertain each other?

10:42.420 --> 10:43.462
Ooh.

10:44.380 --> 10:46.549
- I like that idea.
- Hmm.

10:46.632 --> 10:49.885
Well, maybe I should entertain you first.

10:49.968 --> 10:52.430
If it's the other way around,
I might fall asleep on your thigh again.

10:52.513 --> 10:54.014
[both chuckle]

10:58.144 --> 10:59.937
[vehicle approaching]

11:10.156 --> 11:12.450
What the fuck is your problem, Beau?

11:13.075 --> 11:14.910
Looks like one just rolled up.

11:16.495 --> 11:18.706
Those boys wanted
to prove themselves to you,

11:18.789 --> 11:20.708
and you wouldn't even let them.

11:20.791 --> 11:24.086
I should've known they'd go down
to the bar and cry to you about it.

11:24.169 --> 11:26.088
That's not what happened.

11:26.171 --> 11:28.466
They went down to the bar because...

11:28.549 --> 11:29.967
they drink too much.

11:31.219 --> 11:34.347
And then we bonded over the fact
that you're such an asshole.

11:35.348 --> 11:38.976
You looked me right in the eye
and told me you'd give them a shot.

11:39.059 --> 11:40.603
They had their shot.

11:41.687 --> 11:44.565
And after you and I talked,
I was gonna give them another one.

11:45.649 --> 11:48.527
Then, later that night,
I heard them arguing

11:48.611 --> 11:51.572
about which pet would be
the "most awesomest,"

11:52.490 --> 11:55.493
the cheetah-bear or the shark-dog.

11:56.869 --> 11:59.580
I started thinking about this last year.

12:00.623 --> 12:02.833
How it got so bad we needed a bank loan.

12:02.916 --> 12:04.502
Couldn't even get it approved.

12:06.545 --> 12:08.797
I'm not gonna risk
going through that again.

12:08.881 --> 12:10.674
None of that was their fault.

12:11.174 --> 12:14.428
I need to pay attention
to things here that I can control.

12:16.138 --> 12:18.391
Maybe they had bad luck.

12:19.267 --> 12:21.810
Maybe they were doing
it wrong. I don't know.

12:21.894 --> 12:25.523
But I do know, if I do the job,
it'll get done right.

12:25.606 --> 12:27.816
I thought you might have a good reason.

12:27.900 --> 12:30.278
But it turns out it's just
more of the same shit.

12:30.361 --> 12:33.281
Keeping this place running isn't
good enough a reason for you?

12:33.364 --> 12:35.032
You have a thousand excuses.

12:35.115 --> 12:37.701
"The boys aren't ready, maybe next year...

12:37.785 --> 12:40.120
Rooster's beard spooks the heifers."

12:41.330 --> 12:44.750
As far as you're concerned,
everyone but you is an idiot.

12:44.833 --> 12:46.710
Well, I can't argue with that.

12:47.711 --> 12:49.838
Well, I didn't come here to argue.

12:49.922 --> 12:52.049
I came here to tell you, I'm done.

12:52.800 --> 12:55.844
I'm sick of waiting for you to change.
You won't change for me,

12:55.928 --> 12:57.971
and you're not gonna
change for those boys.

12:58.055 --> 12:59.932
Fine. Here.

13:00.015 --> 13:02.643
It's the divorce papers
and I already signed them.

13:04.395 --> 13:08.732
