finish up in the pasture

13:16.449 --> 13:20.035
and come back to this porch
and realize you are all by yourself.

13:20.578 --> 13:21.620
Sounds good.

13:21.704 --> 13:23.497
Where do I sign up for that?

13:26.750 --> 13:28.168
[engine starting]

13:30.421 --> 13:33.298
[laughs] Okay, that was a lot of fun.

13:33.382 --> 13:35.634
But the next time you want
me to change positions,

13:35.718 --> 13:37.970
you can't just yell out, "Omaha, Omaha!"

13:41.223 --> 13:42.725
Hey, you turned and caught it.

13:45.185 --> 13:47.312
[chuckles] Well, I gotta call a time out,

13:47.396 --> 13:48.647
'cause I got work to do.

13:48.731 --> 13:49.940
- Really?
- Yeah.

13:50.023 --> 13:51.191
What you got to do?

13:51.274 --> 13:53.611
I am subbing for an
English class this week

13:53.694 --> 13:55.738
and they're reading
<i>A Tale of Two Cities.</i>

13:55.821 --> 13:57.948
I haven't read it in years,
so I need to brush up.

13:58.031 --> 13:59.324
- All right.
- [sighs]

13:59.408 --> 14:00.826
Listen, you do...

14:01.744 --> 14:02.828
whatever you got to do.

14:02.911 --> 14:05.539
- [chuckles]
- I just wanna hang out with you. So...

14:05.623 --> 14:08.709
- Oh, that's sweet. Thank you.
- Mmm-hmm.

14:10.419 --> 14:11.670
[sighs]

14:18.552 --> 14:20.012
What are you doing?

14:20.804 --> 14:22.431
Nothing.

14:22.515 --> 14:23.724
Just hanging out.

14:23.807 --> 14:25.934
[chuckling] No, you're watching me read.

14:26.018 --> 14:27.102
Hey, you're good at it, too.

14:27.185 --> 14:28.937
You ain't moving your lips or nothing.

14:29.021 --> 14:30.105
[chuckles]

14:32.065 --> 14:33.609
Okay, you know what?

14:34.610 --> 14:35.653
