something. How about that?

14:37.780 --> 14:39.197
I don't have a TV.

14:40.408 --> 14:41.450
What?

14:41.534 --> 14:42.618
I don't have a TV.

14:42.701 --> 14:43.744
Oh.

14:44.995 --> 14:46.038
Were you robbed?

14:47.498 --> 14:50.167
No. I just... never watched

14:50.250 --> 14:52.090
and it was taking up space,
so I got rid of it.

14:52.961 --> 14:55.801
Okay, I know what all them words
mean separately, but that... [chuckles]

14:57.007 --> 14:59.217
Okay, fine. You know what,
you're reading...

14:59.301 --> 15:01.387
uh... I'll read something, too.

15:01.470 --> 15:03.389
Omaha! Omaha!

15:03.472 --> 15:05.391
