15:05.474 --> 15:07.309
I think you <i>can</i> read.

15:07.393 --> 15:09.853
Oh, come on. I love reading.
It's fundamental.

15:11.104 --> 15:13.190
- All right, what you got here?
- [chuckles]

15:13.273 --> 15:14.650
<i>Three Musketeers.</i>

15:14.733 --> 15:17.110
Why would they write a book
about a candy bar?

15:18.195 --> 15:19.572
What?

15:19.655 --> 15:21.156
No, I'm kidding. [Chuckles]

15:21.239 --> 15:23.409
I know it's based on a movie.

15:24.117 --> 15:27.621
Or we could, uh, just have sex
and I could read this later.

15:27.705 --> 15:30.583
No, come on. This is something
we could do together.

15:30.666 --> 15:32.167
It'll be fun.

15:33.293 --> 15:34.336
Okay, sure, um...

15:34.420 --> 15:35.963
